quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  17,106,"Àti pé al-Ƙur’ān, A ṣàlàyé rẹ̀ (fún ọ) nítorí kí o lè ké e fún àwọn ènìyàn pẹ̀lú pẹ̀lẹ́pẹ̀lẹ́. A sì sọ̀ ọ́ kalẹ̀ díẹ̀ díẹ̀.1 {1}",footnotes:1:Àwọn nasọ̄rọ̄ sọ pé, “Āyah yìí àti sūrah al-’Insān; 76:23 tako sūrah ad-Dukān; 44:3 àti sūrah al-Ƙọdr’;  97:1.”
  17,107,"Sọ pé: “Ẹ gbàgbọ́ nínú al-Ƙur’ān gbọ́ tàbí ẹ kò gbàgbọ́ nínú rẹ̀, dájúdájú àwọn tí A fún ní ìmọ̀ ṣíwájú (ìsọ̀kalẹ̀) rẹ̀, nígbà tí wọ́n bá ń ké e fún wọn, wọn yóò dojú bolẹ̀, tí wọ́n yóò forí kanlẹ̀ (fún Allāhu)."
  17,108,"Wọ́n ń sọ pé: “Mímọ́ ni fún Olúwa wa. Dájúdájú àdéhùn Olúwa wa máa wá sí ìmúṣẹ ni.”"
  18,73,"(Ànábì Mūsā) sọ pé: “Má ṣe bá mi wí nípa ohun tí mo gbàgbé. Má sì ṣe kó ìnira bá mi nínú ọ̀rọ̀ (ìrìn-àjò) mi (pẹ̀lú rẹ).”"
  18,74,"Lẹ́yìn náà, àwọn méjèèjì lọ títí di ìgbà tí wọ́n fi pàdé ọmọdékùnrin kan. (Kidr) sì pa á. (Ànábì Mūsā) sọ pé: “O ṣe pa ẹ̀mí (ènìyàn) mímọ́, láì gba ẹ̀mí? Dájúdájú o ti ṣe n̄ǹkan aburú o.”"
  18,75,"(Kidr) sọ pé: “Ǹjẹ́ èmi kò sọ fún ọ pé dájúdájú ìwọ kò níí lè ṣe sùúrú pẹ̀lú mi.”"
  19,34,"Ìyẹn ni (Ànábì) ‘Īsā ọmọ Mọryam. (Èyí jẹ́) ọ̀rọ̀ òdodo tí àwọn (yẹhudi àti nasọ̄rọ̄) ń ṣeyèméjì nípa rẹ̀."
  19,35,"Kò yẹ fún Allāhu láti sọ ẹnì kan kan di ọmọ. Mímọ́ ni fún Un. Nígbà tí Ó bá pèbùbù kiní kan, Ó kàn máa sọ fún un pé: “Jẹ́ bẹ́ẹ̀.” Ó sì máa jẹ́ bẹ́ẹ̀."
  19,36,"Àti pé dájúdájú Allāhu ni Olúwa mi àti Olúwa yín. Nítorí náà, ẹ jọ́sìn fún Un. Èyí ni ọ̀nà tààrà."
  20,16,"Nítorí náà, ẹni tí kò gbàgbọ́ nínú rẹ̀, tí ó sì tẹ̀lé ìfẹ́-inú rẹ̀, má ṣe jẹ́ kí ó ṣẹ́rí rẹ kúrò níbẹ̀, kí o má baà parun."
  20,17,"Kí ni ìyẹn lọ́wọ́ ọ̀tún rẹ, Mūsā?”"
  20,18,"Ó sọ pé: “Ọ̀pá mi ni. Mò ń fi rọ̀gbọ̀kú. Mo tún ń fi já ewé fún àwọn àgùtàn mi. Mo sì tún ń lò ó fún àwọn bùkátà mìíràn.”"